---
const imgBase = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_IMAGE_BASE;
---

<li class='c-price-card'>
  <div class='c-price-card__content'>
    <div class='c-price-card__image'>
      <img src={`${imgBase}/item-1.jpg`} alt='' alt='' />
    </div>
    <div class='c-price-card__text'>
      <h4 class='c-price-card__title'>
        <span class='c-price-card__title-ja'>
          銘茶五香（ごこう）煎茶・抹茶カステラ詰合せ
        </span>
      </h4>
      <div class='c-price-card__price'>
        ¥
        <span class='c-price-card__price-amount'>10,000</span>
        (税込)
      </div>
      <div class='c-price-card__description'>
        <p>
          森半のスイーツを初めてご利用の方に、人気の3種を詰め合わせてお試しセットです。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='c-price-card__link'>
      <a href='' class='c-link'> 詳しくはこちら </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</li>
